{
  "chapter": 19,
  "chapter_summary": "蓝兰率轿队上山拜见朱五太爷，以美色试探被冷然拒绝，朱五太爷下令任何人越过石阶一步格杀勿论。张聋子试图冲过石阶，被哑巴无舌童子一脚踢死。香香痛哭，临终之际张聋子吐露未尽之言。常无意识破无舌童子身份（西北双哑、天残地缺门下），提出\"杀人者死\"要为张聋子复仇，朱五太爷以万箭埋伏相威胁。蓝兰试图用美色引诱玲珑双剑，令香香脱衣分散注意力，暗中释放暗器却被剑光击落，身陷险境向小马求救。朱五太爷下令杀死轿中人，四名黑衣大汉刀剑齐刺轿子，却被轿中人以内力折断兵刃。朱五太爷又发乱箭，箭头被尽数折回射入窗口。蓝兰终于道出真相：轿中人并非真病，他们上山是为了求药，故意被逼入绝境前来见朱五太爷。轿中年轻人现身，身披貂裘、面色苍白，从容踏过石阶走向珠帘后的朱五太爷，全然无视万箭埋伏。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我叫蓝兰，特地来拜见朱五太爷！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我虽然是个平凡无用的女人，但有时说不定也有能替你老人家效力的地方，只要你老人家盼咐，不管什么事，我都遵命。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "站住！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只不过想看看你老人家的风采，难道连这一点你老人家都不准？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你看见了你面前的石级",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无论谁只要上了这石级一步，格杀勿论！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "你的兄弟有病？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "他病得很重，所以只求你老人家…",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "站住！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "speaker_name": "张聋子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你骗不到我的，你———",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "香香",
      "listener": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "text": "你这是为了什么？",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "speaker_name": "张聋子",
      "listener": "char_xiang_xiang",
      "text": "我实在想不到……想不到我死的时候，居然还有人为我流泪。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "text": "你为什么要这样做？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "speaker_name": "张聋子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "因为…",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好厉害的飞云脚！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他不会说话，他是个哑巴。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "据说江湖中有两个最厉害的哑巴，叫西北双哑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他就是西方星宿海、天残地缺门下的无舌童子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想不到你们还有点见识。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "张聋子能死在这种名人脚下，总算死得不冤。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我说过，无论谁只要越过这石阶一步，格杀匆论！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我还记得你说过的一句话。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "什么话？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杀人者死！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "你想为你的朋友复仇？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你迟早会有机会的，可是现在，你若敢踏上石级一步，我叫你立刻万箭穿心而亡！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "张先生虽然死了，能死在名人手上，美人怀中，也算是死得其所，死而无憾了。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说得好，说得有理。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "人死不能复生，何况每个人迟早都要死的。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "那么你为什么不让你弟弟去死？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "因为他是我弟弟",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "也因为我相信你，—定会护送他平安过山的！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他是个可怜的孩子，从小就多病，连一天好日子都没有过，若是这么样死了，叫我这做姐姐的怎样能安心？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你老人家若是要了他这条命，简直和踩死只蚂蚁一样。所以我只求你老人家开恩放了我们，让我们过山去求医。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也很想放了他、只可惜他不是只蚂蚁，蚂蚁不坐轿子。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他一直躲在轿子里，没有出来拜见你老人家，绝不是因为他敢对你老人家无礼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那是因为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为他实在病得太重，见不得风。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "这里有风？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他为什么不出来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为……因为外面总比轿子里冷得多。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说得好，说得有理。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们替我去把他揪出来，看他死不死得了！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "扫花老人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你是个好男儿，我不想杀你。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren",
      "text": "多谢多谢！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "扫花老人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "我也不喜欢杀人。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren",
      "text": "客气客气！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "扫花老人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "这是什么话？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren",
      "text": "你白天在这里扫花，晚上到哪里去了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "扫花老人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你说我到哪里去了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杀人！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你白天扫花，晚上杀人，这种日子也过得未免太忙了些。你累不累？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "扫花老人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "扫花和杀人都是种乐趣，我怎么会累？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一个人做的若是自己喜欢做的事，就不会觉得累的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "扫花老人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你喜欢干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_sao_hua_de_lao_ren",
      "text": "喜欢打你的鼻子，一拳打不中，还有第二拳，就算打上个三千六百拳，我也不会累的。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位小弟弟，你们今年已经有多大年纪？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们有没有见过一个真正美丽的女人，而且是完全脱光了衣服的？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_xiang_xiang",
      "text": "香香！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_xiang_xiang",
      "text": "你自己认为你自己是不是很难看？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_xiang_xiang",
      "text": "那么你为什么不让他们看看？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们看她美不美？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_long_shuang_jian",
      "speaker_name": "玲珑双剑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "美！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们为什么不多看看？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_long_shuang_jian",
      "speaker_name": "玲珑双剑",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "我们想看你！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我已经是个老太婆了，没什么好看的，可是你们如果一定要看，我……",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我看错了你们，原来你们这里连大带小、连老带少，都不是男人！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小马，你还不快来救我？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们真的忍心杀我？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "留下她！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我要的是轿里的那个人！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_long_shuang_jian",
      "speaker_name": "玲珑双剑",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "要死的，还是要活的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杀！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "果然不出我所料，果然好功夫！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看箭！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "住手！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我早就劝过你们，不要去惹他的，你们为什么不听？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "神龙已现首，阁下又何必再装病？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "text": "他本来就有病！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么病？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "心病。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他病得很重？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "幸好他的病还有药可治！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "治他病的药，并不在山那边！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就在这里，我们就是上山来求药的，所以我们故意要让你把我们逼入绝路、故意要让你认为我们已不能不到这里来！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们千方百计，为的就是要来见我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既然如此，他为什么还要躲在轿子里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我问问他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_nian_qing_ren",
      "text": "朱五太爷想请你出来见见面，你看怎么样？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_nian_qing_ren",
      "text": "你走不走得动？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 520
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nian_qing_ren",
      "speaker_name": "年轻人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在你已看见了我？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来阁下好象真的有病。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nian_qing_ren",
      "speaker_name": "年轻人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可惜你虽然看得见我，我却看不见你。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_wu_tai_ye",
      "speaker_name": "朱五太爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你为何不过来看看？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nian_qing_ren",
      "speaker_name": "年轻人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我正想过去！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 19,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 532
    }
  ],
